description	"Communications Technician

^2Weaponry:
- Plasma Flamethrower ^3[CS1]
-- Uses FP as Fuel

^6Inventory:
- Portable Shield
- Portable Sentry Gun
- Portable E-Web

^3Abilities:
- Kinetic Wave (Force Push 2)

In smaller Imperial outposts, often one or two individuals share the duties of technician, engineer, and tactical support specialist. They rarely engage in active combat, and instead utilize their extensive technical knowledge to give their allies support. When in battle, their technical skills and equipment can come in handy, especially in the case of their Kinetic Gauntlet, something typically used for moving heavy equipment but can be used to reflect large, slow-moving projectiles."

